{"tid":1559864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃國桐律師：警隊非法武力干犯酷刑罪及反人類罪，全球法院有權審判","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:28:19.000Z","uid":276739,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7875d11bf024c71644789ec30c1dfd12a85f6bfd","tid":1559864,"uid":276739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"（一）：擔任反送中義務律師的原因；警察抓人理由主觀，想見被捕者也困難重重；從未想過會送去新屋嶺；香港將變成警察國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oB9YJKFLcLE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoB9YJKFLcLE&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRevhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=42543574\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oB9YJKFLcLE</a><br />\n（二）：每一個示威者都有故事，每一張臉都難忘；為公眾利益而抗爭，有理由不檢控；最黑暗的時候，才見到法律的光芒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0aPxXekWxCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0aPxXekWxCo&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRevhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=aba3c265\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0aPxXekWxCo</a><br />\n（三）：警隊非法武力干犯酷刑罪及反人類罪，全球法院有權審判；上層允許警隊為所欲為，臥底也在犯法；民主國家聲援，香港人不要放棄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-CDYYSj1aAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-CDYYSj1aAw&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRevhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=c4371e01\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-CDYYSj1aAw</a><br />\n黃國桐律師給被捕人士的建議：勿回答任何問題，勿和警察聊天和交心，勿簽文件，勿開手機；如警方要求查看袋子，要問清楚搜查理由；被捕時大聲向旁人講名字<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H6j_WU2Hix8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH6j_WU2Hix8&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRevhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=f40b08dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H6j_WU2Hix8</a>"},{"pid":"9c0e39b3fa41e94838e4f40b051d5765532a9d88","tid":1559864,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67a3b45e04c49829368ad09bd960daeec311d630","tid":1559864,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"846df8279014b5d1fa